OL,3,CLondon Mayor announces plan to cut
OL,4,Cfares on Fridays
OL,6,FThis would require the support of the
OL,7,Fwider rail industry. Peak fares apply
OL,8,Fon weekdays between 6.30am and 9.30am,
OL,9,Fand between 4pm and 7pm, on TfL and
OL,10,Fmainline rail services within .
OL,11,FSomeone commuting by Tube from Zone 6
OL,12,Finto Zone 1 in central London at peak
OL,13,Ftimes currently pays #5.60 per journey.
OL,15,FUnder the trial, this fare would be
OL,16,Fcut by #2 to #3.60 on Fridays. Mr Khan
OL,17,Fis proposing to allocate #24 million
OL,18,Ffrom his budget for the 2024-25
OL,19,Ffinancial year to support the Friday
OL,20,Ftrial.
