OL,3,CLondon Mayor announces plan to cut
OL,4,Cfares on Fridays
OL,6,FIt is hoped increasing the number of
OL,7,Fworkers going to offices on Fridays
OL,8,Fwould raise revenue for the
OL,9,Fhospitality sector through additional
OL,10,Fspending on lunches, after-work drinks
OL,11,Fand evening entertainment. Mr Khan
OL,12,Fsaid he wants "everyone to be able to
OL,13,Fmake the most all week of living or
OL,14,Fworking in London".
OL,16,FHe went on: "London has really bounced
OL,17,Fback since the pandemic, but the lack
OL,18,Fof commuters returning on Fridays is a
OL,19,Fclear exception ` with a major knock-
OL,20,Fon effect on our shops, cafes and
OL,21,Fcultural venues.
