OL,3,CLondon Mayor announces plan to cut
OL,4,Cfares on Fridays
OL,6,F"That's why I've asked TfL to trial
OL,7,Foff-peak fares on Fridays, and I
OL,8,Fencourage Londoners to get involved."
OL,10,FKate Nicholls, chief executive of
OL,11,Findustry body UKHospitality, said:
OL,12,F"There's no doubt that Fridays have
OL,13,Fsuffered as a result of changes to
OL,14,Fworking patterns since the pandemic,
OL,15,Fand hospitality businesses have felt
OL,16,Fthat loss of commuter trade.
